# Foolproof Rice

Serves 2 (ish)

## Ingredients
* 1-1/2 cups water
* 1 cup Basmati rice

## Directions
* Pour the water into a small saucepan, cover with a lid, and set on max heat on a stove
* Once it's boiling, pour in the rice and give it a quick stir
* Immediately turn down the heat to simmer and cover with the lid again
* Set a timer for 12 minutes, and check halfway to give it a stir
* After 12 minutes, give it a stir again and remove from heat - keep covered
* Wait a couple minutes, then its ready!
